Banyana Banyana’s preparations for the 2023 Fifa World Cup get underway in Turkiye. Co-captain Andile Dlamini has more. #dstv403 JOHANNESBURG - Banyana Banyana’s preparations for the 2023 Fifa World Cup get underway in Turkiye. This is despite the devastating earthquake in that country, which has claimed 41,000 lives. READ: Banyana off to Turkiye despite earthquake The hosts and two other countries have pulled out of the tournament in the aftermath of the quake. The other two countries that have withdrawn from participating are Jordan and Venezuela.